about.summary: Functions and datasets for bootstrapping from the book "Bootstrap Methods and Their Application" by A. C. Davison and  D. V. Hinkley (1997, CUP), originally written by Angelo Canty for S.

name: r-boot
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3-25" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-boot
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/boot_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/boot/boot_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 464835fcb453072346ce49e4ae318e04c9dba682349be49db616623b6088fbbe

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('boot')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('boot')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=boot
  license: Unlimited
  summary: Functions and datasets for bootstrapping from the book "Bootstrap Methods and Their Application" by A. C. Davison and  D. V. Hinkley (1997, CUP), originally written by Angelo Canty for S.
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - conda-forge/r
